meaning_str.bing:
v. 出让；转让；出售；售卖
adj. 出售的；销路好的
n. 让人失望的东西
网络. 卖出；销售；出卖

卖；出售；卖出；销售；兜售；推销；促销；售出；交易；出卖；说服…接受；售价为；拍卖；使畅销；使受欢迎
<非正式>销售；出售；推销手段；让人失望地东西

1.en: In a vaguely worded announcement, Repsol reiterated its desire to sell part of its YPF stake, possibly through a public share offering.
1.cn: 在一份措辞含糊的公告中，雷普索尔重申了其出售YPF部分股权的意愿，并表明可能采用公开出售股份的方式。

2.en: Travis: I know you're trying to help, but I'm not willing to sell out.
2.cn: 我知道你是想帮助我，但是我不想为了钱出卖我的事业。

3.en: "We are still trying to sell off the additional linen we had to purchase, " the official complains.
3.cn: “我们现在还在想办法甩卖掉多余的床单，而这是原先要求我们必须购置的，”该官员抱怨道。

0.en: Well, I kinda wanted to sell the cookies.

1.en: I'd like to sell all my clothes, please!
1.cn: 我想把我所有的衣服都卖掉，拜托啦！

2.en: How are you ever going to sell this place?

3.en: I bet we could sell that sign all over Pasadena.
3.cn: 我打赌这种牌子一定能在帕萨迪纳大卖。

4.en: Trust me, this house is gonna sell at Thorpe speed.
4.cn: 相信我，这房子会以索普光速卖出的。

5.en: I know. They probably shouldn't sell those to children.
5.cn: 我懂你。这种产品就不该卖给孩子。

6.en: If we sell them, we will have enough to start a new life.
6.cn: 卖了它们足够我们开始新生活。

7.en: You understand what I'm saying, right? You do sell bonds, don't you, old sport? I'm trying to.
7.cn: 你知道我在说什么，对吧？你是卖债券的，是吧，老伙计？我正在努力卖。

8.en: Miss Rabbit is ill. You've got to sell the ice-cream today. Oh, I am an expert of ice-cream.
8.cn: 兔小姐生病了，今天需要你来替她卖冰淇淋了。哦，我可是很擅长卖冰淇淋的。

9.en: Miss Rabbit is ill. You've got to sell the ice-cream today. Oh, I am an expert of ice-cream.
9.cn: 兔小姐生病了，今天需要你来替她卖冰淇淋了。哦，我可是很擅长卖冰淇淋的。

10.en: I asked you to take care of it. Why on earth would you sell it?
10.cn: 我当时让你妥善保管的，你为什么要卖了它？

11.en: She sells cards and homemade jewels, she said she wanted to sell them. I said, okay. And in one week, I made a $156.
11.cn: 她卖一些卡和自制首饰，她说想卖呢，我答应了，一周里我赚了156美刀。

12.en: Rupert Murdoch should cut me a check for all the papers I sell for him.
12.cn: 默克多得好好谢我帮他卖了那么多报纸。

13.en: And we don't sell drugs, just menus, so the only lie you'll be telling is we print on recycled paper. We don't.
13.cn: 我们不卖药，只卖菜单。所以你唯一要说的谎是我们用再生纸印菜单。其实不是。

14.en: You sell closets and blinds? I could understand shutters and blinds or closets and... We're good, Nancy.
14.cn: 你们卖橱柜和窗帘吗？一般不是卖百叶窗和窗帘 或者橱柜和……我们公司生意很好，南希。

15.en: What are you doing? I can't sell that now. You suck air through your mouth, you moron.
15.cn: 干什么?现在不能卖，用嘴巴吸气，白痴!

16.en: Come on, don't listen to him. Fast Tony would sell his own mother for a grape.
16.cn: 别听他的，火速东尼为了一颗葡萄，连妈妈都肯卖。

17.en: Well, good luck to Dad. Say, how many more boxes would you have to sell in order to win?
17.cn: 那就祝爸爸好运吧，要卖多少盒饼干才能获胜？

18.en: And finish this hellhole so I can sell it. Yeah. I'm sorry about the triplets.
18.cn: 修整好这个鬼地方。我好卖了。好的。对于三胞胎的事我表示遗憾。

19.en: Alicia, don't try to sell me. You are the governor's wife. Your name means something.
19.cn: 艾丽西娅，别把我卖了，你是州长夫人，你的名字意味着些什么。
